# QuickSite Design System

Stripe-inspired, clean, professional. Every page — homepage, dashboard, auth — follows this system.

## Color Palette

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `ocean` | `#635BFF` | Primary brand, buttons, links, active states |
| `ocean-light` | `#7A73FF` | Hover accents, gradient endpoints |
| `ocean-bg` | `#F6F5FF` | Light tinted backgrounds (stats, pricing) |
| `navy` | `#0A2540` | Dark text, dark sections, headings |
| `white` | `#FFFFFF` | Page background, cards |
| `slate-100` | — | Borders, dividers |
| `slate-400/500` | — | Secondary text, labels |
| `emerald-500` | — | Success states |
| `red-500` | — | Error states, destructive actions |
| `amber-500` | — | Warning states |

**Legacy tokens** (`primary`, `charcoal`, `nude`, `gold-soft`) — avoid in new code. Use `ocean` and `navy` instead.

## Typography

| Element | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Page heading | `font-noto text-3xl font-black text-navy` |
| Section heading | `font-noto text-[2.75rem] font-black leading-[1.15] text-navy` |
| Card title | `font-noto text-base font-bold text-navy` |
| Body text | `font-sans text-sm text-slate-600` |
| Muted text | `text-sm text-slate-500` |
| Label | `text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy/60` |
| Logo | `font-logo font-bold` |
| Numbers / stats | `font-noto font-black text-navy` |

**Rules:**
- `font-noto` for all headings (Hebrew). Never use `font-display` for Hebrew text.
- `font-sans` (Assistant) for body and UI text.
- `font-logo` (Space Grotesk) only for the QuickSite logo.

## Buttons

### Primary
```
rounded-full bg-ocean px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white
transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-ocean/85 cursor-pointer
```

### Secondary
```
rounded-full border border-slate-200 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-navy
transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-ocean hover:text-ocean cursor-pointer
```

### Ghost (on dark backgrounds)
```
rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white/50
transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-white/30 hover:text-white/75 cursor-pointer
```

### Destructive
```
rounded-full bg-red-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white
transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-red-600 cursor-pointer
```

**Rules:**
- Always add `cursor-pointer` to interactive elements.
- All buttons use `rounded-full` for pill shape.
- Consistent padding: `px-5 py-2.5` standard, `px-8 py-3.5` for hero CTAs.
- Use `group` + arrow icon for CTA buttons with directional arrows.

## Inputs & Forms

### Text Input
```
w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-navy
placeholder:text-slate-300
focus:border-ocean focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-ocean/30
```

### Select
```
w-full cursor-pointer rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-navy
focus:border-ocean focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-ocean/30
```

### Textarea
```
w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm text-navy
placeholder:text-slate-300 resize-none
focus:border-ocean focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-ocean/30
```

### Label
```
mb-1.5 block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy/60
```

### Field Error
```
mt-1 text-xs text-red-500
```

**Rules:**
- Inputs always use `rounded-lg`, NOT `rounded-full`.
- Use consistent padding `px-4 py-3` for all input types.
- `dir="ltr"` on email, phone, URL fields.
- Validation with Zod in server actions. Show inline errors below fields.

## Cards

### Light card (on white/light bg)
```
rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7
transition: background-color 200ms, border-color 200ms, box-shadow 200ms
hover:border-ocean/25 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-ocean/[0.06]
```

### Dark card (on navy bg)
```
rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.04] p-6
hover:border-ocean-light/20 hover:bg-white/[0.06]
```

### Dashboard panel
```
rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6
```

