## Icons

**Use Lucide React exclusively.** Do NOT use Material Symbols Outlined or any icon font.

```tsx
import { FileText, Globe, Zap } from 'lucide-react';
// Standard size in UI: h-4 w-4
// Card/feature icon: h-[18px] w-[18px]
// Section accent icon: h-6 w-6
```

Icon containers:
```
inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-ocean/[0.08]
```

## Layout

### Dashboard Sidebar
- Fixed right `w-64`, white bg, `border-l border-slate-100`
- Nav items: `rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-500`
- Active: `bg-ocean/10 text-ocean font-bold`
- Logo: `font-logo font-bold text-navy`, Q badge `bg-ocean text-white`

### Dashboard Content Area
- `p-4 pt-16 md:mr-64 md:p-6 md:pt-6 lg:p-8`
- Page heading followed by content with `mt-8`

### Section Backgrounds
- Light sections: `bg-white` or `bg-ocean-bg`
- Dark sections: `bg-navy text-white`
- Always use `border-t border-slate-100` between same-color sections

## Motion & Transitions

- Hover: `transition-colors duration-200`
- Cards: `transition: background-color 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease`
- Entrance: `hp-enter` class (CSS-only, 0.7s ease-out translateY)
- NO infinite animations, NO 3D transforms, NO heavy glows
- Always add `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` for entrance animations

## Dark Sections Pattern

```tsx
<section className="bg-navy px-6 py-24 text-white md:py-32">
  <p className="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-light">Label</p>
  <h2 className="mt-4 font-noto text-3xl font-black">Heading</h2>
  <p className="mt-6 text-white/50 leading-relaxed">Body</p>
</section>
```

## Empty States

```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-200 p-12 text-center">
  <Icon className="mb-4 h-10 w-10 text-slate-300" />
  <h3 className="font-noto text-base font-bold text-navy">Title</h3>
