```

## Auth Pages (Login / Register / Password Reset)

iBot-inspired flat design. Split layout: white info panel (right in RTL) + form on `#f6f7fb` bg.
- Inputs: `rounded-xl border-[#d0d4e4]`, focus ring `ring-ocean/10`
- Buttons: `rounded-xl` (NOT `rounded-full` like dashboard)
- Decorative circles: subtle gradient circles at corners (`from-ocean/5`, `from-emerald-500/5`)
- Features: 3 items with colored round icons (emerald, purple, amber)
- Logo icon floats with `animate-[float_3s_ease-in-out_infinite]`

## Email Templates

All emails use shared `layout()` from `lib/email.ts`:
- Background: `#f6f7fb`, white card `border-radius: 16px`
- Header: gradient bar `#635BFF → #7A73FF` with logo
- Content: RTL, Hebrew, `Segoe UI` font
- CTA buttons: `#635BFF`, `border-radius: 12px`
- Fire-and-forget: always `.catch(console.error)`, never await in critical path

## Anti-Patterns

- ❌ `bg-primary`, `text-charcoal`, `border-charcoal/10` → use `bg-ocean`, `text-navy`, `border-slate-200`
- ❌ Material Symbols icon font → use Lucide React components
- ❌ `font-display` for Hebrew headings → use `font-noto font-black`
- ❌ `rounded-md` or `rounded-lg` on buttons → use `rounded-full`
- ❌ `hover:opacity-90` → use `hover:bg-ocean/85` (explicit color shift)
- ❌ Inconsistent input padding → always `px-4 py-3`
- ❌ `useEffect` for data fetching → server components
- ❌ Loading spinners for page data → server-side fetch
- ❌ `confirm()` for destructive actions → use a styled confirmation dialog
- ❌ `await sendEmail(...)` in action critical path → use fire-and-forget `.catch(console.error)`
- ❌ Blocking user flow on email failure → emails must never break the main action
